ooks?id=0PihzVU0oRIC&pg=PA408&lpg=PA408&dq=ministro+de+la+presidencia+costa+rica+1978&source=bl&ots=pdUbnHcBM_&sig=Cw8AXTJmLE-k7m88tcYvgu1QMhE&hl=es&sa=X&redir_esc=y#v=onepage&q=ministro%20de%20la%20presidencia%20costa%20rica%201978&f=false|access-date=30 November 2016|language=Spanish}}</ref>\n|rowspan=2|[[National Liberation Party (Costa Rica)|National Liberation Party]]\n!rowspan=2 style=\"background:{{National Liberation Party (Costa Rica)/meta/color}}|\n|rowspan=2|<center>[[File:Daniel Oduber 3 (adjusted).jpg|50px]]</center>\n|rowspan=2|[[Daniel Oduber Quir\u00f3s]] \n|-\n! style=\"background:{{National Liberation Party (Costa Rica)/meta/color}}| {{color|white|4}}  \n||<center>[[File:Fernando Volio Jim\u00e9nez.jpg|50px]]</center>||Fernando Volio Jim\u00e9nez||1977-1978\n|-\n! ! style=\"background:{{Social Christian Unity Party/meta/color}}| {{color|white|5}}  \n||<center>[[File:No_image.svg|50px]]</center>||Jos\u00e9 Rafael Cordero Croceri||1978-1982<ref>{{cite book|last1=Carazo Odio|first1=Rodrigo|title=Carazo; tiempo y marcha|url=https://books.google.co.cr/books?id=iESmZzyNlCoC&pg=PA293&lpg=PA293&dq=ministro+de+la+presidencia+Jos%C3%A9+Cordero+Croceri&source=bl&ots=RhU7HAtUWW&sig=GJXee-L6dOOCfD4Oxef7M0y-yD0&hl=es&sa=X&redir_esc=y#v=onepage&q=ministro%20de%20la%20presidencia%20Jos%C3%A9%20Cordero%20Croceri&f=false|access-date=30 November 2016|language=Spanish}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Intercambio de figuras importantes: visitas de costarricenses a Corea|url=http://cri.mofa.go.kr/webmodule/htsboard/template/read/legengreadboard.jsp?typeID=16&boardid=14039&seqno=687398&c=&t=&pagenum=1&tableName=TYPE_ENGLEGATIO&pc=&dc=&wc=&lu=&vu=&iu=&du=|access-date=30 November 2016|language=Spanish}}</ref>\n|[[Unity Coalition]]\n! style=\"background:{{Social Christian Unity Party/meta/color}}|\n|[[File:Rodrigo Carazo Odio.jpg|50px]]||[[Rodrigo Carazo Odio]]\n|-\n! style=\"background:{{National Liberation Party (Costa Rica)/meta/color}}| {{color|white|6}}  \n||<center>[[File